casebody.data:
Tuesday, May 30, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-637. Middletown v. Butler Cty. Bd. of Commrs. Butler County, No. CA94-03-084.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of court of appeals’ order setting aside injunction granted by the common pleas court,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, granted, effective May 26, 1995.
